{"tid":2016733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家知唔知我地挨打緊,8千個手足日日心驚膽跳比人告坐監,嘈小兩句盡做,就算1%機會都用100%心去盡做","createTime":"2020-05-14T15:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T03:27:25.000Z","uid":179775,"like":101,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"9b7dc19b95060d834642a74fa35cfdec718b68fe","tid":2016733,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T15:15:49.000Z","msg":"35+又嘈話無用，你唔撚做點知有無用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7up又話無用，9做，咁可唔可以做左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你做完無用最多都係浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但到時有用，但你無做你後悔都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日日睇住手足比人突然告重罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己都睇到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗下當時人會點，見到你地為咩鳩白兵嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過試盡一切可行辦法幫手足好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n家下可唔可以就算得0.001%機會都拎100%心去盡做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以用互相欣賞各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係咩都話無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日開始可唔可以多一分支持小一嘴質疑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇見你哋火都嚟"},{"pid":"b5b0a2c759cc98dcd3f0426ff58e605c0f5b8aac","tid":2016733,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T15:16:40.000Z","msg":"借個位唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抗爭疲勞?無力感?內鬥?...係因為你地唔記得咗一樣野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2016723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2016723</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c5111bb88087da352d03726b8730902c93a34b03","tid":2016733,"uid":192824,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T15:22:45.000Z","msg":"兒子亦對外面資訊甚感期待，例如連登熱門帖文，「有一期同佢哋話，出面依家拗緊『鬥黃』，仔仔就話，『唔係呀？咁多手足坐喺入面，出面竟然有精力講呢啲嘢？』」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200510/7U7DWN2QCZMYXIH77K23OOMTFU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200510%2F7U7DWN2QCZMYXIH77K23OOMTFU%2F&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7jYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=9c474852\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200510%2F7U7DWN2QCZMYXIH77K23OOMTFU%2F&h=ac9d0ac8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200510/7U7DWN2QCZMYXIH77K23OOMTFU/</a>"},{"pid":"77e6ca7967586604815db859d7e2522c085f3ee1","tid":2016733,"uid":113074,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T15:25:51.000Z","msg":"condom仔唔去進攻功能組別走去掟汽油彈<br />\n戇鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e520b646c519f0f4991d572335c0517a64130b","tid":2016733,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T15:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5b1661b428529612c3105a9176393c8dba7330","tid":2016733,"uid":113074,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T15:28:16.000Z","msg":"流亡手足記得9月返嚟投票呀<br />\n輸咗唯你是問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2eeb80f7ab2db6150775d2e2b85da7a9992db30","tid":2016733,"uid":179775,"like":1